sing <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/mobile/\">a mobile app</a> to post a quick photo. Either way, here are four free <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/\">WordPress</a> themes that handle blogging just fine, but know how to get out of the way when you want to feature your photos.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-11092\" title=\"screenshot\" src=\"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/screenshot.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/adventure-journal\"><strong>Adventure Journal</strong></a> is a powerful, feature-rich theme that lets you customize a wide variety of features from the comfort of your Dashboard.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-11100\" title=\"screenshot\" src=\"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/screenshot1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/matala\"><strong>Matala</strong></a> is a colorful textured theme.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-11101\" title=\"screenshot-1\" src=\"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/screenshot-11.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/modularity-lite\"><strong>Modularity Lite</strong></a> is a minimally styled photo theme with a homepage slideshow.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-11102\" title=\"screenshot-2\" src=\"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/screenshot-21.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/twentyeleven\"><strong>Twenty Eleven</strong></a> is sophisticated, lightweight, and adaptable.</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/weblogtoolscollection/UXMP/~4/kkWsufaxAkM\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\