p NYC!  Not only are we one of the companies sponsoring the event, but we will also have THREE members of our team speaking at the event!  <a href=\"http://webdevstudios.com/2012/05/10/wds-sponsoring-speaking-attending-wordcamp-nyc-2012/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"April Heline\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1412:\"<p><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-6642\" title=\"wcnyc-attending-250\" src=\"http://webdevstudios.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/wcnyc-attending-250.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" />This year WebDevStudios is going to very busy while attending WordCamp NYC!  Not only are we one of the companies <a href=\"http://2012.nyc.wordcamp.org/2012/04/10/sponsor-spotlight-webdev-studios/\">sponsoring the event</a>, but we will also have THREE members of our team speaking at the event! This year <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/williamsba\">Brad Williams</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/ericandrewlewis\">Eric Lewis</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/mtoppa\">Mike Toppa</a> will all be presenting on various WordPress topics.  We will be sure to fill you all in on each of their topics once we get a little closer to the event!</p>\n<p>For those of you that are interested in attending WordCamp NYC it will be held on June 9th and 10th at Baruch College. It will include over 60 sessions in 2 days of WordPressy goodness.</p>\n<p>To buy tickets and find out more information check out the WordCamp NYC website at <a href=\"http://2012.nyc.wordcamp.org/\">http://2012.nyc.wordcamp.org/</a> or follow them on Twitter at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/wordcampnyc\">WordCampNYC</a> and the hashtag <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/search/realtime/%23wcnyc\">#wcnyc</a>. We hope to see you all there!</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"http://webdevstudios.com/2012/05/10/wds-sponsoring-speaking-attending-wordcamp-nyc-2012/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"WebDevStudios is Attending WordCamp San Diego 2012 This Weekend!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:100:\"http://webdevstudios.com/2012/03/23/webdevstudios-is-attending-wordcamp-san-diego-2012-this-weekend/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:109:\"http://webdevstudios.com/2012/03/23/webdevstudios-is-attending-wordcamp-san-diego-2012-this-weekend/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 23 Mar 2012 16:40:38 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"ca