/271985246242399\' class=\'uibutton confirm\'>Event on Facebook</a><br><br><img src=\"http://profile.ak.fbcdn.net/hprofile-ak-snc6/276740_271985246242399_1547772003_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"img\" />Caribbean food and English-language comedy followed by a DJ dance party at the Scandals bar in Prenzlauer Berg. Entry is free. (The entry fee is included in your first, 3-euro drink--beer, wine or non-alcohol.)\n\nSit out on the sidewalk tables in warm weather, step inside for some of Berlin\'s best English-language comedy, and later dance to funk, soul and R&amp;B. As always, an international crowd. Your lovely host will be there to help break the ice and ensure the private-party atmosphere where it\'s easy to talk and meet people. Party starts 7pm with the buffet. At 9pm the comedy begins and runs until the DJ takes over at 10. \n\nThe Menu: Trini Style!!!... (Trinidad and Tobago Cuisine) \nSoup with dumplings (gemuse suppe mit teig bällchen) \nDeviled eggs (gefüllte eier) \nSurprise salad (Frisch Porree salad) \nCoconut Bake (Brot Teig gebacken mit cocosnuss)\n\nThe comedians:\nPaul Salamone (US):\n<a rel=\"nowfollow\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&amp;v=Q8OKG8Kgo_I\">youtube.com/&hellip;</a>\nCaroline Clifford (UK):\n<a rel=\"nowfollow\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wIrqyn1gx0Y\">youtube.com/&hellip;</a>\nChris Davis (Scotland):\n<a rel=\"nowfollow\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7KOelAKHtFc\">youtube.com/&hellip;</a>\nDavid Deery (US - tentative):\n<a rel=\"nowfollow\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0gZLx24C7Kc\">youtube.com/&hellip;</a>\n\nSee you there!\nCharles\n25 32 89 78\n0163-52 72 213\n\nDirections: Scandals is located at: Lychener Straße 18, 10437 Berlin. It\'s a short walk up Danzigerstraße from the U-2 Eberswalder U-Bahn. Then left on Lychener. The M-10 Tram also stops nearby, and from Prenzlauer Allee (Ring) S-Bahn it\'s a 10-minute walk. <!-- owner: 696657358 venue:  -->','Summer Fusion Party ','','pu