dy show at my friends pancake house. \n\nI\'ll do a marathon 13 hours of jokes all about pancakes! \n\nThat of course is bullshit, but I will do a show. I mean, what\'s a \"show?\"\n\nI\'ll sit in front of people and tell stories. \n\nNot much of a show, but hey, it\'ll be cheaper than a plate of pancakes, so come out. \n\n<!-- owner: 1080921294 venue:  -->','The MF David Deery Funny Pancake Spectacular. ','','publish','open','open','','the-mf-david-deery-funny-pancake-spectacular','','','2012-10-02 10:53:33','2012-10-02 08:53:33','',0,'http://comedyinenglish.de/ai1ec_event/the-mf-david-deery-funny-pancake-spectacular/?instance_id=',0,'ai1ec_event','',0),(644301,1,'2012-10-02 10:53:33','2012-10-02 08:53:33','<a href=\'https://www.facebook.com/events/144105415721312\' class=\'uibutton confirm\'>Event on Facebook</a><br><br><img src=\"http://profile.ak.fbcdn.net/hprofile-ak-snc7/373703_144105415721312_2128200086_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"img\" />Laughing Cows – the comedy night with an all-female line up - is back in Berlin this spring with top UK comic Jo Caulfield performing alongside resident MC, Maureen Younger.\n\nBest-known for her legendary one-woman shows, Jo Caulfield is “one of the finest female comics at work” (The Observer) and was recently nominated as “the best female Stand-Up in the UK” (Chortle.co.uk). “She is, quite simply, a damn funny woman” (The Scotsman). Jo is also a regular guest on popular British TV programmes, Mock The Week (BBC2) and Have I Got News For You (BBC1).\n\nMaureen Younger is the resident MC of Laughing Cows in London, Birmingham and Berlin. In May Maureen will compere Crying with Laughter - a major charity night in the West End of London which will feature some of the UK’s top female comics including Jo Brand, Jenny Éclair and Shazia Mirza. Maureen is also a contributor on BBC radio and regularly gigs in Berlin in both English and German.\n\nSo if you are looking for a night of stand up comedy direct from the UK, then Laughing Cows is the night for you.\n\nTickets are 10.00€, Students 8.00€. For Reservations call 030 48 62 31 86 or e-mail londonlaughs@yahoo.co.uk.\n<!-- owner:  venue:  -->','Laughing Cows - Comedy Direct from the UK  - with Jo Caulfield','','publish','open','open','','laughing-cows-comedy-direct-from-the-uk-with-jo-caulfield','','','2012-10-02 10:53:33','2012-10-02 08:53:33','',0,'http://comedyinenglish.de/ai1ec_event/laughing-cows-comedy-direct-from-the-uk-with-jo-caulfield/?instance_id=',0,'ai1ec_event','',0),(644302,1,'2012-10-02 10:53:33','2012-10-02 08:53:33','<a href=\'https://www.facebook.com/events/171367269656247\' class=\'uibutton confirm\'>Event on Facebook</a><br><br><img src=\"http://profile.ak.fbcdn.net/hprofile-ak-snc7/373433_171367269656247_1712320286_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"img\" />The Impronauts (David Cassel, Michela Bellino,Katy Kavanaugh, Mara Leibowitz, and Harvey Rabbit) are back! Come watch a one-act play built from audience suggestions form in front of your eyes! Who knows what will happen? We sure don\'t! Join us at T Berlin (<a rel=\"nowfollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tberlinkreuzberg\">facebook.com/&hellip;</a>) every Friday in May @ 20:30 and join in the fun! 5€ entrance.\n\nLive music and open stage to follow!!!  Do you have something you want to perform?  Talk to Harvey or David<!-- owner: 548124967 venue:  -->','Friday Night Impro at T Berlin with The Impronauts','','publish','open','open','','friday-night-impro-at-t-berlin-with-the-impronauts','','','2012-10-02 10:53:33','2012-10-02 08:53:33','',0,'http://comedyinenglish.de/ai1ec_event/friday-night-impro-at-t-berlin-with-the-impronauts/?instance_id=',0,'ai1ec_event','',0),(644303,1,'2012-10-02 10:53:33','2012-10-02 08:53:33','<a href=\'https://www.facebook.com/events/351989051521177\' class=\'uibutton confirm\'>Event on Facebook</a><br><br><img src=\"http://profile.ak.fbcdn.net/hprofile-ak-snc7/373450_351989051521177_821329039_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"img\" />The Impronauts will mak